{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-item-js","path":"/projects/apollo-express-kontent-boilerplate","result":{"data":{"kontentItemProject":{"system":{"id":"030aa085-896b-4a73-b3e7-efea080654bf"},"elements":{"title":{"value":"Apollo Express Kontent boilerplate"},"release_date":{"value":"2018-12-12T00:00:00Z"},"source_code_url":{"value":"https://github.com/Kentico/kontent-boilerplate-express-apollo"},"live_url":{"value":"https://kontent-boilerplate-apollo.herokuapp.com"},"summary":{"value":"<p>This boilerplate showcasing how to combine the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\">Node.js</a>&nbsp;web server <a href=\"https://expressjs.com/\">Express.js</a>&nbsp;with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a>. The server converts the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.kontent.ai/reference/kentico-kontent-apis-overview\">Kentico Kontent Delivery REST API</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a>&nbsp;using the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com/\">Apollo framework</a>&nbsp;and then renders the output using the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pugjs.org/\">Pug view engine</a>.</p>"},"image":{"value":[{"url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/68c8a1f3-3cf6-4d12-bcf6-1f773b508543/schema.png","width":1914,"height":966,"description":null}]},"content":{"value":"<p>Boilerplate is combining <a href=\"https://expressjs.com\">Express.js</a> web server with <a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com\">Apollo framework</a> middleware to provide a GraphQL API wrapper around the REST API by headless CMS Kentico Kontent.</p>\n<figure data-asset-id=\"d39726b9-1606-4fd0-9fac-a681708f8be2\" data-image-id=\"d39726b9-1606-4fd0-9fac-a681708f8be2\"><img src=\"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/68c8a1f3-3cf6-4d12-bcf6-1f773b508543/schema.png\" data-asset-id=\"d39726b9-1606-4fd0-9fac-a681708f8be2\" data-image-id=\"d39726b9-1606-4fd0-9fac-a681708f8be2\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>GraphQL schema is automatically generated using the<a href=\"https://github.com/Kentico/kontent-schema-generator-graphql\"> Kontent Schema generator tool</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To showcase using the Apollo GraphQL client, the boilerplate is loading the last three articles stored in headless CMS and using <a href=\"https://pugjs.org\">Pug view engine</a> to construct the view of this simple listing.</p>\n<figure data-asset-id=\"52a16ca5-902f-4d67-9900-82512019d997\" data-image-id=\"52a16ca5-902f-4d67-9900-82512019d997\"><img src=\"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/e0f51f6e-515e-40e4-b1aa-24979d6aff1a/template_thumbnail.png\" data-asset-id=\"52a16ca5-902f-4d67-9900-82512019d997\" data-image-id=\"52a16ca5-902f-4d67-9900-82512019d997\" alt=\"\"></figure>","modular_content":[],"images":[{"image_id":"d39726b9-1606-4fd0-9fac-a681708f8be2","url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/68c8a1f3-3cf6-4d12-bcf6-1f773b508543/schema.png","width":1914,"height":966,"description":null},{"image_id":"52a16ca5-902f-4d67-9900-82512019d997","url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/e0f51f6e-515e-40e4-b1aa-24979d6aff1a/template_thumbnail.png","width":821,"height":916,"description":null}]}}}},"pageContext":{"language":"en-US","codename":"apollo_express_boilerplate_utilizing_headless_cms"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2624379000","690649307"]}